1 Data retrival

1.1 Twitter API
Downloading the 2000 most recent tweets containing the words “affitti” or “affitto” in the last week

tw <- search_tweets(q = "affitti|affitto",n = 2000,type="recent",include_rts = F,lang="it")

twPIU <- make.tweet.df(tw)

1.2 Reddit API
Downloading threads andcomments in the last month

RDt<-find_thread_urls(keywords = "affitti", sort_by = "comments", period = "month") 

RDt<- RDt %>% mutate(ID=1:nrow(RDt),.before=1)

#lemmatizazione + eliminare le stopword italiane
dfCorpusLem <- lemmaUDP(x = twCLEAN$col4,
                        model = modello,
                        stopw = tm::stopwords("it"),
                        userstopw = c("affitto","affitti","NA"))



txtLem <- dfCorpusLem %>%
  filter(!is.na(dfCorpusLem$lemma) & dfCorpusLem$STOP == FALSE & upos %in% c("ADJ","NOUN")) %>%
  select(doc_id, lemma) %>%
  group_by(doc_id = as.numeric(doc_id)) %>%
  summarise(txtL = paste(lemma, collapse = " "))

          # 2.5 is the size of the most frequent words
          # 0.5 is the size of the least frequent words

We take only observation of Repubblica (Pre covid), then we procede vectorizing the dataset

# reduce matrix
tdm.r <- removeSparseTerms(tdm,sparse = 0.95)
# transform in a matrix object
mtdm.r <- as.matrix(tdm.r)
# compute distances
dst.tdm <- dist(mtdm.r,method = "cosine")
# Hierarchical Cluster
hhAc <- hclust(d = dst.tdm, method = "ward.D2")
# plot dendrogram
par(mar=c(1,2,2,1))
plot(hhAc, hang = -1,sub = "", cex=0.5,
     main="Hierarchical Cluster Pre Covid (cosine - Ward)",
     cex.main=0.9, xlab="", cex.axis=0.6, cex.lab=0.2)

fviz_dend(hhAc, k = 11,
          k_colors = alphabet2(n = 11),
          type = "phylogenic",
          repel = TRUE,
          phylo_layout = "layout.gem") +
  ggtitle("Dendrogram Repubblica Pre Covid")

# library with function silhouette
vSilIn <- c()
for(i in 2:20){
  vSilIn <- c(vSilIn,mean(silhouette(x = cutree(hhAc,k = i),dist = dst.tdm)[,3]))
}
data.frame(n.clust=2:20,silhouette=vSilIn) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=n.clust,y=silhouette))+
  geom_line(color="blue",size=1.5)+geom_point(size=2,color="blue")+theme_light()+
  ggtitle("Silhouette score Pre Covid")

nclu <- 9 # number of clusters
clust <- cutree(hhAc,k = nclu)
